</table>
</div>
<p local-id=3D"29740a2a3b06">Document metadata returned by <code>GET /sessi=
ons/{id}/documents</code> must include a <strong>person identifier</strong>=
 and <strong>role</strong> for each document record, attributing every coll=
ected document to the specific individual who provided it within the sessio=
n.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"4635dee6-b69e-4a84-8f77-f51507a37e17">
<h3 local-id=3D"6285b2ea4cc5" id=3D"EmbeddableUIforKYC/KYB-Returned-for-Cor=
rectionsFlow">Returned-for-Corrections Flow</h3>
<p local-id=3D"5be2c98385b4"><strong>Resolved =E2=80=94 Annotated Re-Entry<=
/strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"34299bb42eda">Reviewer notes are surfaced inline. All prior =
data is preserved. Resubmission triggers a new verification run.</p>
<p local-id=3D"69ced6dcaf8e">Correction supports two outcomes:</p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"bef9a55f-f1b6-4f49-b1f8-e61cce8f35ba">
<li local-id=3D"9ab29339-7c36-477a-97d5-2cb891798b6c">
<p local-id=3D"8235e98277e5">The end user successfully resubmits and a new =
verification run is triggered.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"0ce0f682-4a07-4ce3-937b-9314471442e8">
<p local-id=3D"6622352b02ed">The session is finally rejected and no further=
 resubmission is permitted.</p></li>
</ol>
<p local-id=3D"77e90bb3e240">Resubmission emits <code>flow:submitted</code>=
.</p>
<p local-id=3D"d973a578d3f3">See the <strong>Resolved Decisions Log</strong=
> for the full correction flow description.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"c60af2dc-5c66-429c-ab2f-5ccbfdf3fcd6">
<h2 local-id=3D"df6e3e9c9f42" id=3D"EmbeddableUIforKYC/KYB-TechnicalRequire=
ments">Technical Requirements</h2>
<h3 local-id=3D"d7f48120e829" id=3D"EmbeddableUIforKYC/KYB-EmbeddingArchite=
cture">Embedding Architecture</h3>
<p local-id=3D"595a4383f864">Served in an iframe at <code>{client}.interro.=
co</code>.</p>
<p local-id=3D"19bd2d27a85a"><strong>Resolved =E2=80=94 iframe:</strong> Th=
e embedding architecture will use an iframe. The component renders at a fix=
ed mobile-friendly width with internal scroll. The host application is resp=
onsible only for embedding the iframe and allocating space =E2=80=94 no res=
ize coordination is required. This approach minimizes integration complexit=
y and ensures a consistent experience across desktop and mobile.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"d3c8f264-3512-4ba3-a437-f4c8304d61eb">
<h3 local-id=3D"12bfd9fbb4dc" id=3D"EmbeddableUIforKYC/KYB-SessionandStateM=
anagement">Session and State Management</h3>
<h4 local-id=3D"e64611d12779" id=3D"EmbeddableUIforKYC/KYB-Auto-SaveandDura=
bility">Auto-Save and Durability</h4>
<ul local-id=3D"5941dcb6-bc03-4736-9c04-5b896a5bf90f">
<li local-id=3D"40f7611a-8d8f-42ca-9509-c81820341ab5">
<p local-id=3D"697abd356e20">Server-side auto-save</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"9063c279-4b80-4787-92d3-6399c7967b9f">
<p local-id=3D"886d845df755">Cross-device resume</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d087d216-6915-47e6-b6e1-1cb822f37bcc">
<p local-id=3D"73a24d3fdec2">Resume =E2=89=A4 3 seconds</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"505ac54b99eb"><strong>Resolved =E2=80=94 Session Lifetime:</=
strong> Sessions remain resumable for <strong>30 days</strong>.</p>
<p local-id=3D"ec8f7f2fc300"><strong>Sensitive Data Handling:</strong> Sens=
itive information will be asterisked in the UI.</p>
<h4 local-id=3D"bf4efcaefb65" id=3D"EmbeddableUIforKYC/KYB-UBOOwnershipThre=
shold">UBO Ownership Threshold</h4>
<p local-id=3D"e4f321d21b13"><strong>Resolved ---- </strong>UBO Threshold i=
s 25%, see the resolved decision log below for details.</p>
<h4 local-id=3D"804ca2872889" id=3D"EmbeddableUIforKYC/KYB-SessionTokenExpi=
ry">Session Token Expiry</h4>
<blockquote local-id=3D"0eaf6f9b-bd84-4f8e-bd35-7490bbe273a1">
<p local-id=3D"7c77a199dbc4"><strong>Open Question =E2=80=94 Session Token =
Expiry</strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"948f38afdd98">Recommendation: Session access tokens for the =
embedded component expire after 60 minutes and are refreshable by the host =
application. Standalone verification link tokens expire after 72 hours and =
are not refreshable =E2=80=94 a new link must be generated via the resend m=
echanism. All tokens are single-session; opening a session on a new device =
invalidates the prior token.</p>
<p local-id=3D"8b4aadc60648"><strong>Note:</strong> Revisit the token expir=
y =E2=80=94 consider making it stricter.</p>
</blockquote>
<h4 local-id=3D"3c4f02dacbea" id=3D"EmbeddableUIforKYC/KYB-ConcurrentSessio=
nBehavior">Concurrent Session Behavior</h4>
<p local-id=3D"b4ca40a51eae"><strong>Resolved =E2=80=94 Last-Write-Wins:</s=
trong> If the same user opens the flow on multiple devices, the most recent=
 save takes precedence. No conflict detection is applied.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"78d3dfd1-30ba-41e5-8667-5620d6baedc6">
