<hr local-id=3D"0cdc59ef-b980-4e14-9563-e0d1b983b4f5">
<h2 local-id=3D"b00b6885f990" id=3D"EmbeddableUIforKYC/KYB-Post-MVPRoadmapI=
tems">Post-MVP Roadmap Items</h2>
<h3 local-id=3D"d47452046fbe" id=3D"EmbeddableUIforKYC/KYB-OCRDocumentQuali=
tyGate">OCR Document Quality Gate</h3>
<p local-id=3D"e69442f86540">Employ an OCR image quality gate on entity doc=
uments collected when they are uploaded by the user, to ensure they are rea=
dable. The user should not be able to continue until the uploaded documents=
 pass this threshold, which may take a few seconds. <strong>Not an MVP requ=
irement.</strong></p>
<h3 local-id=3D"78b4a620871e" id=3D"EmbeddableUIforKYC/KYB-ConfigurableDocu=
mentCollectionperContextID">Configurable Document Collection per Context ID=
</h3>
<p local-id=3D"97316824e351">Be able to ingest additional entity documents =
required for a specific Context ID received from the application. If a GP n=
eeds additional documentation to collect, there should be an API endpoint t=
o configure certain document uploads per Context ID. <strong>Not an MVP req=
uirement =E2=80=94 Phase 2.</strong></p>
<hr local-id=3D"7d6e6c7a-6aee-4795-a32b-c5ef48e0bcee">
