<td data-local-id=3D"0f8d368b-30b3-4b2d-a6c4-de82d8988e9b" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"6cd9183ede8c"><strong>Primary user completing IDV for additi=
onal persons</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"47ef31d5-ce6b-4891-a780-c8a394d6b68b" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"5fa9a0b68417">"Verify Now" button available per additional p=
erson so that the primary user can begin IDV on behalf of an additional per=
son if the additional person is nearby</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"4d8cafe2-9186-411f-b0ea-6914e0f7b0fd">
<td data-local-id=3D"ed1beea0-4a0c-4c1c-a75d-735fc41d25fe" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"5c75f9287e67"><strong>Correction flow</strong></p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"1c5d83f7-a473-49c3-80dd-e51da0464078" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"af8b0c73173c">Annotated re-entry. After an end user complete=
s their verification and results are sent to Verivend: a reviewer decides t=
he end user must edit a detail. The reviewer enters notes in the Verivend a=
dmin UI where their review happens. Interro ingests the notes. The end user=
's verification session is reopened with all prior information saved. The r=
eviewer's note is displayed so the end user knows what to change. The end u=
ser can edit their information and documents and resubmit.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"82e023f4-0785-4fe0-88d1-2adfc4c099ba">
<td data-local-id=3D"c45e71e1-01f3-4390-a3c8-0773fcf1a000" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"864cc689053a"><strong>Session lifetime</strong></p></td>
